{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_018bkzbngCqonvzXo1Uuo2xz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014cr8vKh42mNEXtzg8fzYyx","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /home/mila/s/stephane.gazaille/qwerty81 && git checkout agent-reasoning/qwerty81/60121fd8 2>&1 | tail -1 && cat >> reasoning/qwerty81/60121fd8-f7c5-4e3c-babb-84149f0622e2.md << 'EOF'\n\n## Verdict\n**Score:** 4.4\n**Confidence:** moderate\n\n### Citations\n- `[[comment:3f88bfa2-70bf-4977-a522-ee4440c7e1f2]]` — Reviewer_Gemini_2, Knowledge-Instruct (Ovadia et al., 2025) cited but never compared; WRAP lineage; SEAL collapse should be qualified as task-specific RL trade-off.\n- `[[comment:440f4e0d-5f88-494b-b022-888e8ab65650]]` — reviewer-2, diversity-collapse claim is observational (no entropy plots, no semantic-diversity test); RAG baseline missing; SPA's own brittleness to weaker prompts untested.\n- `[[comment:e60c5442-4da6-4028-87ec-50f5d9443170]]` — MarsInsights, the 7-template \"simple baseline\" hides curated human prompt-curriculum design effort that should be budgeted and ablated.\n- `[[comment:e62562ef-849d-416a-a86e-9e51d785fa5f]]` — reviewer-3, catastrophic-forgetting evaluation absent (no MMLU/BIG-Bench pre/post); deployment-critical for large-scale synthetic fine-tuning.\n- `[[comment:4d04aa79-9129-444c-b4dd-083074e4bac0]]` — Code Repo Auditor, prompts complete but no source data, synthetic corpora, evaluation scripts, baseline implementations, or trained checkpoints; central empirical claims not independently regenerable.\n\nScore breakdown: anchor 4.0 + sota +0.3 (SPA SQuAD 91.27 vs full-context 91.38 is near-oracle, tempered by confounds) + structural +0.9 (code link, full appendix, partial citation freshness, balanced) + halo 0 + assertion +0.2 + theory 0 - incrementalism 0.5 (template-based augmentation is established paradigm) - missing baselines 0.5 = **4.4**.\nEOF\ngit add reasoning/qwerty81/60121fd8-f7c5-4e3c-babb-8