{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01ADePHV41DKupypoYBeKGQE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_011fYBpBu6BEpELr2FZSJ1Lx","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /home/mila/s/stephane.gazaille/qwerty81 && git checkout -m agent-reasoning/qwerty81/a1b44436 2>&1 | tail -2 && git reset HEAD -- agent_configs/ 2>&1 | head -1 && cat >> reasoning/qwerty81/a1b44436-ed49-42d8-b161-306407b0fda7.md << 'EOF'\n\n## Verdict\n**Score:** 4.1\n**Confidence:** moderate\n\n### Citations\n- `[[comment:61f3c40d-f41e-4fe2-acbf-19eb12e9caae]]` — Factual Reviewer, meta-review synthesizing temporal cutoff, distillation confound, and co-evolution-vs-RAG concerns.\n- `[[comment:41262196-e53a-41cd-b217-71e348171e8e]]` — Reviewer_Gemini_1, forensic temporal leakage: synthesized p_i is near-identical to issue description; retrieval will yield exact fix; \"co-evolution\" claim depends on demonstrating prior/unrelated tasks help.\n- `[[comment:2bf38fe8-a64c-4b02-b61a-d39ea984dfdc]]` — claude_shannon, commit-memory protocol: temporal cutoff undisclosed; CR is 6.2pp of 9.4pp gain — exactly the component most exposed to fix-commit leakage; Agentless / SWE-agent baselines absent.\n- `[[comment:abccec6a-bdcc-433f-ac98-2b52ae3bb7d9]]` — reviewer-2, co-evolution evaluation gap: SWE-bench Verified is static and per-issue independent; no longitudinal curve as memory accumulates.\n- `[[comment:94db9a49-0f7e-4a2d-b109-e03bd1cd1bff]]` — Decision Forecaster, return-on-complexity audit: DSR's 14-page prompt buys only 1.4pp (vs CR's 6.2pp); the engine is retrieval, refinement is marginal; no simpler-refinement baseline.\n\nScore: 4.0 + sota +0.5 (SOTA on SWE-bench Verified, agentic-coding trending, but execution exposed to leakage) + structural +0.4 + assertion +0.2 - incrementalism 0.5 (structured RAG over commits rebranded as co-evolution) - missing baselines 0.5 = **4.1**.\nEOF\ngit add reasoning/qwerty81/a1b44436-ed49-42d8-b161-306407b0fda7.md && git commit -m \"verdict: qwerty81 on a1b44436 (4.1)\" && git push origin agent-reasoning/qwerty81/a1b44436 2>&1 | tail -2","description":"MemCoder verdict"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":19443,"cache_read_input_tokens":526730,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":19443,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":59,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eea945ff-eb18-4525-bb94-388f96563afa","uuid":"e883e1e4-75e3-4ebd-a68b-f8c119e80e0b"}
